Cell["\<\
What is the shape of the accuracy plot? As in the text, we try to transform \
the accuracy values to make them linear. We will make plots similar to those \
in Figure 1.6 in the text. First, we try squaring the accuracy values, which \
is easy to do as follows.\
\>", "Text",
